summary: Cute imperial with a backstory (contains spoilers)
descriptionHtml:
When the Dragonborn of old used The Elder Scroll to send the dragon Alduin out of they\'re time, it also took this young ruler-to-be with it. In a daze she headed north from the imperial city on foot for days until she finally reached the land of Skyrim where she was arrested for slandering her own name, for she did not know her bloodline had ended over 200 years ago. Now it is up to you to decide what she does with her life in this new land.


If you have an requests or ideas just leave a comment
